  "body": "<div align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/BKw2JZQj/6f52c0ab982b253705acbb7296acb662.gif\" alt=\"NexusDev Network Banner\" width=\"100%\">\n  <br><br>\n  <p>\n    <a href=\"https://discord.gg/XhqAfHx7yE\">\n      <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1263430459564621874?color=5865F2&label=Join%20our%20Discord&logo=discord&logoColor=white&style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Join our Discord\">\n    </a>\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<hr>\n\n<div align=\"center\" style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 20px 0;\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/kVNQvKGm/nexusdev-logo.png\" alt=\"NexusDev Network\" width=\"150\">\n  <h2>🎉 GRAND OPENING: NexusDev Network!</h2>\n  <p><b>Join our brand new Minecraft network!</b></p>\n  <p>Featuring cutting-edge custom gamemodes:</p>\n  <p>\n    <b>⚔️ Arc Raiders</b> | <b>🏛️ Civ 7</b> | <b>💀 SMP Hardcore</b> | <b>🤠 Wild West RP</b>\n  </p>\n  <p><b>Server IP:</b> <code>mc.nexusdev.cc</code></p>\n</div>\n# Overview\nNexusCore is the library require to use all Nexus Development Studio plugins.\n\n# Features\n- Custom language translations\n- Auto Updater\n- Analytics\n- Remote Support\n- Server dump\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <p><b>Real-time statistics powered by <a href=\"[https://bstats.org/plugin/bukkit/NexusCore/23015](https://bstats.org/plugin/bukkit/NexusCore/23015)\">bStats</a></b></p>\n  \n  <a href=\"https://bstats.org/plugin/bukkit/NexusCore/23015\">\n    <img src=\"https://bstats.org/signatures/bukkit/NexusCore.svg\" alt=\"bStats Servers\">\n  </a>\n  \n  <p><i>Trusted by networks worldwide • Updates every 30 minutes</i></p>\n</div>",
